title: Howard Stern Presents Train Performs Led Zeppelin II
description:
Howard Stern Presents Train Performs Led Zeppelin II  (47:31)

The multi-platinum-selling Train perform the legendary "Led Zeppelin II" album in its entirety LIVE at Irving Plaza in New York City as an homage to one of their biggest musical inspirations.

* Whole Lotta Love
* What Is and What Should Never Be
* The Lemon Song
* Thank You
* Heartbreaker
* Living Loving Maid (She's Just a Woman)
* Ramble On
* Moby Dick
* Bring It On Home
